ActImmigration and Refugee Protection Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Immigration and Refugee Protection Regulations
PrecisRegulations Amending the IMMIGRATION AND REFUGEE PROTECTION REGULATIONS in order to improve the fiscal sustainability of the parents and grandparents program over the longer term and avoid future backlogs, while ensuring those who are able to provide for their sponsored parents and grandparents continue to be reunited with them.
